{"tid":1099563,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[畫葡撻］人同食物有咩分別","createTime":"2019-04-10T00:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T05:15:04.000Z","uid":132425,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f7bf6d8ba8ee766b9e69d6b28da87472a19b0564","tid":1099563,"uid":132425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbAK3bN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbAK3bN.png&h=436b60bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物競天擇弱肉強食<br />\n特別係香港 一個以錢為核心價值嘅社會<br />\n人對人好多時候都變咗用錢衡量<br />\n私樓仔 公屋仔 <br />\n為咗錢可以去到幾盡呢？<br />\n道德上 其實損害其他人利益 冇乜人會大大聲認同<br />\n但私底下 其實只係保障緊自己利益<br />\n如果有一個損人利己 而冇後果嘅機會 有幾多人會實行？<br />\n<br />\n一啖咬落去個葡撻嘅時候<br />\n有幾多人睇唔倒 又有幾多人扮睇唔倒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorryfor1999<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/painting_of_him/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpainting_of_him%2F&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=fa4399ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/painting_of_him/</a>"},{"pid":"96d60717958d758d7739d04b4617f076d404ec25","tid":1099563,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"Gchi樓主<br />\n係咪油畫<br />\n個lighting同酥皮做得好好"},{"pid":"cc04f9028fcd341f83d1599426a864c05309d47e","tid":1099563,"uid":132425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"96d60717958d758d7739d04b4617f076d404ec25","tid":1099563,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"Gchi樓主<br />\n係咪油畫<br />\n個lighting同酥皮做得好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"用咗塑膠彩<br />\n多謝Gchu!"}]}